item.title: Khuda mere
item.description: Lyrics Intro I know the way I walking was wrong, That you were never with me oh my God! And now I want you to edify my thoughts, cause, You will be my destiny, I want you to be my destiny, Please be my destiny… Bekarar he, Betab he, Bejaan si yeh jindagi, Betaal me kyun chal rahi? Ae Khuda…. tu he kaha? Meri aashaa, mera jahaan… Verse 1 Tujhe dhundta he,
